nodes.text: A female individual was a Jedi Master at some point in time prior to 41 ABY. In 41 ABY, when New Jedi Order Grand Master Luke Skywalker visited the Jedi enclave on the planet Corellia, a picture—made before Grand Master Skywalker visited the enclave—of the Jedi Master meditating was on one of the enclave's walls.
The female Jedi Master first appeared albeit picture only in Aaron Allston's novel Legacy of the Force: Betrayal, the first entry in the Star Wars: Legacy of the Force series.
